g.text: DataflowConfigure different event sources Event Hubs to subscribe to an event grid topic.Triggers event sources from various scenarios, including different actions performed on the event sources.Use Event Grid to support the events coming from different Azure services.Leverages different event handlers (Azure Functions, Logic Apps, Blob Storage) to handle different use cases.Use different types of actions to handle the result of the event handlers, like Blob Storage, automation to drive demand shaping on the app and to trigger eco-mode.
